          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " isn't a bad game, it's just that in a genre that's been flooded with more and more titles thanks to the resurgence of farming/life sims, you are expected to do something to stand out that's not just a gimmick on the pre-existing formula. That being said, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Monster Harvest",
            "type": "text",
