            "text": " ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "is",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " a fun game to explore if you enjoy the genre and are looking for a bit more of a casual experience and no time pressure of trying to get everything done within a day. You can  pick up the game and enjoy growing the planimals on the go if you want a different take on the farming/life simulation genre as there is still an enjoyable game here.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
